{"tid":1317334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝連城廣場mos burger","createTime":"2019-07-14T18:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T18:31:52.000Z","uid":37924,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"51dab105093a9cc71006fdafe16a1b6d7b11c582","tid":1317334,"uid":37924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:16:54.000Z","msg":"發夢係新城市打狗<br />\n上左2樓回氣 冇水冇物資得把遮 見到有個女仔拎住杯台式飲品<br />\n問佢&quot;依! 仲有開呀?!&quot; 未等佢答我就轉身走<br />\n點知落左半閘 去左旁邊mos burger<br />\n我 : 想問下仲有冇野飲賣<br />\n店員1:冇啦收左工<br />\n店員2:水要唔要?<br />\n我 : 要呀要呀唔該你 你地一陣要小心d 冇路走<br />\n店員: 辛苦哂你地 我地都要留係到看鋪<br />\n之後一杯極大杯既冰水就到左我手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連番多謝後就行番出去<br />\n<br />\n見番個飲台式飲品既女仔<br />\n女仔: 你係唔係想飲? 我飲左小小咋<br />\n我舉一舉隻大杯講左句唔洗喇多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日我真係好自豪我係沙田人"},{"pid":"1876a7aa15a3f216289281cd3194a211ecff8d83","tid":1317334,"uid":37924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:20:48.000Z","msg":"得閒番去食下野先"},{"pid":"dd08e9c8bc88a533f79ec4933de39bef946507cd","tid":1317334,"uid":36722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:21:27.000Z","msg":"巴打保重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39573cb71d5166835b7064f53c46e94b0e4d419","tid":1317334,"uid":37924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd08e9c8bc88a533f79ec4933de39bef946507cd","tid":1317334,"uid":36722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:21:27.000Z","msg":"巴打保重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:22:55.000Z","msg":"訓教發夢珍咩重?"},{"pid":"0ea3aa722a1d6349593bc99051352b266e8e6937","tid":1317334,"uid":37924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d39573cb71d5166835b7064f53c46e94b0e4d419","tid":13